data.title: The 81st anniversary of the sinking of the Polish destroyer ORP 'Kujawiak'
data.meta_description: On 15th of June we celebrate the 81st anniversary of the sinking of the Polish destroyer ORP 'Kujawiak' off the coast of Malta. Polish Ambassador to Malta Tomasz Czyszek and Consul Łukasz Felczak laid a wreath commemorating this tragedy at the plaque at the Upper Barrakka Gardens in Valletta.
data.text:
On 15th of June we celebrate the 81st anniversary of the sinking of the Polish destroyer ORP 'Kujawiak' off the coast of Malta. Polish Ambassador to Malta Tomasz Czyszek and Consul Łukasz Felczak laid a wreath commemorating this tragedy at the plaque at the Upper Barrakka Gardens in Valletta.
